Some PPAs under CY 2019 20% Development Fund do not partake the nature of investment or capital expenditures, such as:
(1) Conduct of collection, transport and proper disposal of segregated wastes; 
(2) Operation and Maintenance of Materials Recovery Facility (MRF);
(3) Operation and Maintenance of the Sanitary Land Fill;
(4) Protection and Maintenance of Reforested areas in the Co-Ma Areas/Local Conservation Area; and
(5) Rehabilitation, operation and maintenance of Municipal Nursery
